To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private ConcealedBabySwallow _concealedbabyswallow;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_concealedbabyswallow = ConcealedBabySwallow(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_concealedbabyswallow.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "concealedbabyswallow", _concealedbabyswallow.Current.Value);
}
